                        <interp inst="t18500708-name-610" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18500708-name-610" type="surname" value="KENCHAT"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18500708-name-610" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM KENCHAT</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, G</hi> 199). I took Fletcher into custody on another charge, and found on him this pocket-book and two papers.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18500708-name-611" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18500708-name-611" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
